I'll jump out of anon to answer this.
The reviews will be random. My first intention is to focus on older and shortrr material that i rarely (or never) see mentioned. Don't be shocked if something released in the past year comes up; while I am not playing favorites, I am not aiming to do two reviews every two weeks. Even at the pace I write, it is exhausting.
